FX.25 test vectors.

Test vectors are embedded directly in the Rust test code (src/fx25/tests.rs)
rather than as external files, for build simplicity. The vectors exercise:

- All 15 valid FX.25 correlation tags
- Encode/decode roundtrip for each tag
- RS error correction at various error rates
- Shortened RS codes (tags 0x06-0x0D)
- Receiver state machine bit-level processing
- Known AX.25 frame encoding compatible with direwolf's implementation
